sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as K8s API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP TLS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Controllers
    participant RouteAPI as OpenShift Route API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as KServe Predictor<br/>80/443 TCP
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Gateway as Gateway<br/>(openshift-ai-inference)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>mTLS

    Note over User,Predictor: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (RawDeployment Mode)
    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate/Validate<br/>TLS (OpenShift serving cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>Auth: SA Token
    Controller->>RouteAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor,<br/>PodMonitor, ClusterRoleBinding
    Note right of Controller: Route: Edge or Reencrypt TLS<br/>based on auth annotation

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Predictor: External Client Request Flow
        User->>Router: GET/POST model endpoint<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS (Edge/Reencrypt)
        Router->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>HTTP/80 or HTTPS/443
        Predictor-->>Router: Prediction Response
        Router-->>User: JSON Response
    end

    Note over User,Authorino: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService with Gateway API Auth
    User->>K8sAPI: POST LLMInferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate LLMInferenceService<br/>TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy (Kuadrant)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (Istio)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Roles & RoleBindings<br/>Auth: SA Token

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over User,Authorino: External Client via Gateway API
        User->>Gateway: Request model endpoint<br/>HTTPS/443
        Gateway->>Authorino: Auth check<br/>mTLS (via EnvoyFilter)
        Authorino-->>Gateway: Auth decision
        Gateway->>Predictor: Forward (authorized)<br/>HTTP/80
        Predictor-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>User: JSON Response
    end

    Note over User,NGC: Flow 3: NIM Account Integration
    User->>K8sAPI: POST Account CR + API Key Secret<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate Account<br/>TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    Controller->>NGC: Validate API Key<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
    NGC-->>Controller: Key valid + Model Config
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Pull Secret,<br/>Runtime Templates,<br/>NIM ConfigMap

    Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 4: CA Certificate Bundle Management
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch: odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>openshift-service-ca.crt
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update<br/>odh-kserve-custom-ca-bundle
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Recreate storage-config<br/>to pick up new certs
